title: "NVIDIA (NVDA) Up 243% YTD: Will It Carry Momentum in 2024?"
text: "NVIDIA (NVDA) stock is likely to carry the upward momentum in 2024 on hopes that the company will be a prime beneficiary of growing investments in generative AI."

title: "4 ETF Areas & Stocks to Win on Upbeat November Retail Sales"
text: "Retail Sales in the United States increased 4.1% year-on-year in November 2023
source_name: marking the strongest annual growth since February
date: following a downwardly revised 2.2% gain in October."

title: "TomTom Develops In-Car Voice AI Assistant With Microsoft"
text: "Mapping/navigation company TomTom says it has developed an artificial intelligence (AI)-powered
source_name: in-car conversational assistant in collaboration with Microsoft. The tool offers enhanced voice interaction with infotainment
sentiment: and arrives at the end of a year that saw voice AI integrated into more and more applications."
